name: Morph7
description:
Morph7 is an original, edition of 20, video artwork by FLUQS. It is part of a series which focusses on the interplay between transitioning objects and textures, complex behaviour and symmetry, development and repetition. Each work is a short loop, but if watched over a longer period of time different layers of subtleties and details emerge.

File info: 1080x1080 mp4, 30 fps, 4 seconds
